text: Denis Tabako (born 20 February 1974) is a Belarusian rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Belarus Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Minsk
